<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Redemption Request Rejected</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }
        .container {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            border-bottom: 3px solid #FF6B35;
            padding-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .logo {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #FF6B35;
        }
        .content h1 {
            color: #d63031;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .deal-info {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-left: 4px solid #d63031;
        }
        .deal-info h3 {
            margin-top: 0;
            color: #333;
        }
        .deal-info p {
            margin: 5px 0;
            padding: 5px 0;
        }
        .deal-info strong {
            color: #d63031;
        }
        .rejection-reason {
            background-color: #fff5f5;
            border: 1px solid #fed7d7;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .rejection-reason h3 {
            color: #c53030;
            margin-top: 0;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #FF6B35;
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 30px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 10px 0;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 30px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #eee;
            text-align: center;
            color: #666;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .status-rejected {
            color: #d63031;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 18px;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 10px;
            background-color: #fff5f5;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .helpful-tips {
            background-color: #e8f4fd;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .helpful-tips h3 {
            color: #0066cc;
            margin-top: 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <div class="logo">Indians in Ghana</div>
            <p>Exclusive Deals & Offers</p>
        </div>

        <div class="content">
            <h1>‚ùå Redemption Request Rejected</h1>
            
            <p>Dear {{fullName}},</p>
            
            <p>We regret to inform you that your recent redemption request has been rejected.</p>

            <div class="status-rejected">
                STATUS: REJECTED
            </div>

            <div class="deal-info">
                <h3>üìã Redemption Details</h3>
                <p><strong>Deal:</strong> {{dealTitle}}</p>
                <p><strong>Business:</strong> {{businessName}}</p>
                <p><strong>Redemption ID:</strong> {{redemptionId}}</p>
                <p><strong>Request Date:</strong> {{requestDate}}</p>
                <p><strong>Membership Number:</strong> {{membershipNumber}}</p>
            </div>

            {{#if rejectionReason}}
            <div class="rejection-reason">
                <h3>üìù Reason for Rejection</h3>
                <p>{{rejectionReason}}</p>
            </div>
            {{/if}}

            <div class="helpful-tips">
                <h3>üí° What You Can Do</h3>
                <ul style="color: #333; padding-left: 20px;">
                    <li>Contact the business directly to clarify any requirements</li>
                    <li>Ensure you meet all terms and conditions of the deal</li>
                    <li>Check if the deal is still valid and within the redemption period</li>
                    <li>Submit a new redemption request if the issue has been resolved</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
                <a href="{{dealsUrl}}" class="button">Browse More Deals</a>
            </div>

            <div style="background-color: #f8f9fa; padding: 15px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 20px 0;">
                <h3 style="color: #333; margin-top: 0;">üìû Need Help?</h3>
                <p>If you believe this rejection was made in error or if you have questions about the redemption process, please contact our support team.</p>
                <p><strong>Support:</strong> support@indiansinghana.com</p>
            </div>

            <p>We appreciate your understanding and look forward to helping you redeem deals successfully in the future.</p>

            <p>Best regards,<br>
            <strong>Indians in Ghana Team</strong></p>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>This notification was sent regarding your redemption request on the Indians in Ghana platform.</p>
            <p>You can manage your account and view deal history by logging into your dashboard.</p>
            <p style="margin-top: 15px;">
                <small>¬© 2025 Indians in Ghana. All rights reserved.</small>
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>